# Personal Portfolio Website

A clean and responsive personal portfolio website built using HTML and CSS.  
This project showcases profile information, skills, and contact details in a structured layout.

## 📌 Features

- Semantic HTML structure
- Clean and minimal UI
- Responsive layout design
- Organized sections (About, Skills, Projects, Contact)
- Styled header and footer

## 🛠 Technologies Used

- HTML5
- CSS3

## 🚀 How to Run

1. Download or clone the repository.
2. Open the HTML file in any modern web browser.

No additional setup required.

## 🎯 Purpose

This project was created to practice:
- Website structuring
- Layout design
- Styling fundamentals
- Responsive design basics

